@startuml

!theme plain
top to bottom direction
skinparam linetype ortho

interface Product << sealed >> {
  +name() : String
  +description() : String
  +price() : BigDecimal
  +type() : ProductType
}

class ProductDecorators {
  +{static} DISCOUNTED : UnaryOperator<Product>
  +{static} TAXED : UnaryOperator<Product>
  +{static} GIFT_WRAPPED : UnaryOperator<Product>
}

note top of ProductDecorators
  Functional Decorator: each decoration is a first-class
  UnaryOperator<Product> value that rebuilds the immutable
  common.Product through the ProductType factory. Decorations
  compose with andThen - the same composition theme as
  factory, visitor and builder - and reuse common directly.
end note

ProductDecorators -[#595959,dashed]->  Product : "«UnaryOperator<Product>»"
@enduml
